    public class MaterialImageCropper
extends gwt.material.design.client.ui.MaterialImage
implements gwt.material.design.client.base.JsLoader, HasCropEvents
    A simple Image Cropping addin component.

    XML Namespace Declaration

      xmlns:ma='urn:import:gwt.material.design.addins.client'

    UiBinder Usage:

      <ma:cropper.MaterialImageCropper ui:field="cropper" url="some.png" />

 
    Java Usage:
    
 
      cropper.addCropHandler(event -> MaterialToast.fireToast(event.getResult()));
   cropper.crop();
    Author:
    kevzlou7979
    See Also:
    Material Image Cropper, Croppie 2.5.0
